== Overview ==
The Marauder class quadra chassis is a formidable offensive platform. Multiple weapon slots and exceptional armour make it the greatest power available to controllers. The Marauder towers over other bots and as a result can inflict more damage with better aim. All of this firepower however comes at the cost of shields and speed.

Sells for 63280 credits.

